      {
        "type": "network",
        "path": "/proc/122177/ns/net"
      },
      {
        "type": "ipc",
        "path": "/proc/122177/ns/ipc"
      },
      {
        "type": "uts",
        "path": "/proc/122177/ns/uts"
      },
      {
        "type": "mount"
      },
      {
        "type": "cgroup"
      },
      {
        "type": "user"
      }
    ],
```

The user namespace should also have the path set to the infraContainer as for the network, ipc and uts namespaces.
